channel.title: What could have possibly caused this? [317]
channel.description:
Revision: 317 Source: Delta
It seems for some strange reason some of my classes have stopped working. clickingMost (works for a few in-game buttons), potions (none of the case(s) work). Now I've come to the conclusion it must be something with the new handler's I've been making for my source. I've made custom agility (being the most recent), Herblore, started a Firemaking class, and everything was good until I reached the last class I made. The agility one. I'm sure this problem can be fixed, but I just don't know, nor understand how-to. Would someone please mind elaborating on the problem, and possibly explain a fix? Any [b]HELP[/b] is appreciated. Thank you.
Edit: Could it be as simple as me having to update my java? I'm using 7, build 51.
Compiling error:
